subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
lead_paragraph: Connecticut Coach Geno Auriemma is vying for his eighth N.C.A.A. women’s title. Coach Jeff Walz is trying to beat UConn for the first time in his six years at Louisville.
